  "summary": "Malicious code in ethereum-input-decorder (PyPI)",
  "details": "The typosquatted package installs a Mythic/Poseidon C2 framework beacon and ensures persistence. After installation, the beacon communicates with C2 on wegoexchange[.]site for further commands.\n\n\n---\n\nCategory: MALICIOUS - The campaign has clearly malicious intent, like infostealers.\n\n\nCampaign: 2026-07-tennacity\n\n\nReasons (based on the campaign):\n\n\n - typosquatting\n\n\n - Downloads and executes a remote executable.\n\n\n - The package contains code to detect if it is running in a sandbox environment.\n\n\n - malware\n\n\n - persistence\n\n",
